Author

OVERVIEW 

- The challenge

  Users should be able to:
    - View the optimal layout for each page depending on their device's screen size
    - See hover states for all interactive elements
    - Navigate between the homepage and the location page

- Links
    - Figma design: https://www.figma.com/design/v7N49IeLjrJ34hIzYMa4Ek/art-gallery-website?node-id=2-72&p=f&t=gGbiFMIV1fTKcalh-0
    - GitHub: https://github.com/Argoneo

- My process
  - Built with
    - Semantic HTML5
    - CSS3 (flexbox and grid)
    - Vanilla JavaScript
    - Mobile-first workflow

- What I learned
  This project allowed me to reinforce responsive layout techniques using pure CSS and better organize my HTML structure. I also handled basic JavaScript interactivity, such as dynamic hover states via addEventListener.

